            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had to take my ward to hospital as he was not well and has gone to school just to write the exam. As a guardian I have to wait outside the school for 1 hour in hot sun. I had called reception and concerned teachers several times but all calls went unanswered. When spoken to reception to kindly connect to principal since no one else is answering the calls the request was outrightly dismissed.\nSchool Management needs to wake up. Even the Information to the child was not passed.\n\nThe child was denied medical treatment also in the school",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
